Synopsis

Kaiko Itsuki (五いつ木き カイコ, Itsuki Kaiko) is the Anti-Demon Corps' 5th Unit Vice-Chief.

Kaiko wears a hairband that organizes her long hair down behind her shoulders. She wears a standard Anti-Demon Corps uniform.
